thread.title: Bobby Mills
thread.title_full: PRO Import Tuners.com reviewed by Bobby Mills

author: Bobby Mills
title: Bobby Mills
text:
Extremely courteous company who cares where your money is going and if your parts are correct before shipment - thus saving lots of extra time/hassle in case the wrong parts were selected.
Oscar called me about my first order with them to verify that my order was correct and validated my identity without giving too much information away. They wanted to make sure that I really was going to spend $500+ on new wheels being that this was my first time using them.
The wheels came within a week in excellent condition and I'm stoaked to get them mounted.
Cheers to a great company.
